summary:
Here’s a toast to my best friend! She don’t care about the he said she said 👯‍♀️🍾🥂
Hey @taylorswift these two beautiful faces...
caption:
Here’s a toast to my best friend! She don’t care about the he said she said 👯‍♀️🍾🥂
Hey @taylorswift these two beautiful faces will be seeing you in 48 days!!! And I thought I’d take a moment to tell you about our friendship. We met in German class my first year, her second, at Temple University. We admitted to each other years later that we were both trying to become friends with another girl in the same class 😂 our friendship was literally an accident. Over the past 6 years, she has been my therapist, wing woman, player 2 and everything in between. She helped through the tough times and I helped her through hers. Even after I moved half way around the world, we are still as close as two best friends could possibly be. She is the Abigail to my Taylor and I am beyond grateful to have her in my life 💖

blog.title: Elizabeth...
blog.description:
Dear followers,

Thank-you for visiting my blog, I hope you find something you like here, and enjoy browsing. 
I do say although my blog is safe for work, I do post nudity and art which might be inappropriate for those sensitive to nudity and for minors, which is why 21+ only please. if your blog is of a pornographic nature please unfollow me thanks, there is a difference between sexy and sex and quite frankly it's subjective so it's best to be clear. I have no hard feelings against your choices, and if I want to look at porn I know how to find it on my own thanks. However I don't mind you saving images of a public nature from my blog and posting them as your own, I'm not going to throw a hissy fit over users stealing my images, they're free from the Internet and as long as the images are not owned by me or of me feel free to blog away. 
I'm respectful of your choices please be respectful of mine. xoxo
